@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_whxnis(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.exp((v1 * (tmp + 0.15 + tmp + 0.62)))
    v0 = (wp.abs((v0 + 0.70 * tmp + 0.62)) + ((v0 + 0.19 / v2 + 0.83) * (v1 + 0.43 + tmp + 0.94)))
    v0 = wp.exp(((tmp + 0.97 * tmp + 0.47) * 0.58))
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.cos((v2 + 0.15 / tmp + 0.30)))
    data[tid] = v0
